name: IR - Insatiable run
description:
Controls:
Space or LMC - jump / restart on GameOver.

Plot:
You are very hungry bean on morning on a morning run!
Eat everything you see and jump over brown things.
But remember - you are what you eat!!!
(...game endless...)

Special for MigJam #6!
Engine:   KaboomJS (https://kaboomjs.com/)
Art:   https://kaboomjs.itch.io/
Music:  https://joshuuu.itch.io/
SFX:   https://sfxr.me/
